ck">\r\n                        </div><!--\r\n                        --><div class="col-md-8 vcenter col-sm-8 col-xs-8 col-lg-8"> \r\n                            <p>Place your weight through the crutches as you step down with your good leg.</p>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>', '				<div class="col-md-12">\r\n                    <p class="subtitle-content">Going upstairs using crutches</p>\r\n                    <p class="cursive-text">The Good go to heaven... Up with the good!</p>\r\n                    <p>It doesn''t matter how you remember how the good leg leads this movement just as long as you do!</p>\r\n                    <p>Start close to the bottom step and then :<br></p>\r\n                    <div class="row">\r\n                        <div class="text-center col-md-4 vcenter col-sm-4 col-xs-4 col-lg-4"> \r\n                            <img src="img/good-leg.png" class="img-responsive center-block">\r\n                        </div><!--\r\n                        --><div class="col-md-8 vcenter col-sm-8 col-xs-8 col-lg-8"> \r\n                            <p>Place your weight through your crutches, bring your good leg up to the next step, let your bad leg trail behind.</p>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class="text-center col-md-4 vcenter col-sm-4 col-xs-4 col-lg-4"> \r\n                            <img src="img/injured-leg.png" class="img-responsive center-block">\r\n                        </div><!--\r\n                        --><div class="col-md-8 vcenter col-sm-8 col-xs-8 col-lg-8"> \r\n                            <p>Straighten your good leg and bring your bad leg and</p>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class="text-center col-md-4 vcenter col-sm-4 col-xs-4 col-lg-4"> \r\n                            <img src="img/crutches.png" class="img-responsive center-block">\r\n                        </div><!--\r\n                     